Class AbstractSearch<E,K extends java.util.Comparator<E>>

java.lang.Object
  search.methods.AbstractSearch<E,K>
Type Parameters:
E - the element to search for
K - the applicable comparator of the list
Direct Known Subclasses:
AVLSearch, BinarySearch, BSTSearch, InterpolationSearch, SequentialSearch
public abstract class AbstractSearch<E,K extends java.util.Comparator<E>>
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract Class holds the common characteristics of the search methods and also provides an abstraction for the methods to be used as one abstract super class
